Lattice-BP++ — License, Provenance & Patent Notice
==================================================

SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 The Soqucoin Core developers / Soqucoin Labs Inc.

Original work by Soqucoin: a lattice-based Bulletproofs++ construction (range
proofs, ring signatures, stealth addresses, commitments) for confidential,
post-quantum transactions. Licensed under the MIT License; the full license text
is in the repository root `COPYING`.

The NTT twiddle factors and Montgomery/Barrett reduction constants follow the
CRYSTALS-Dilithium NIST reference values (public domain; see
`src/crypto/dilithium/LICENSE`). This module is otherwise not derived from
third-party source code.

